config SUNXI_TVTOP
	tristate "Allwinner H713 TV Subsystem Top Module"
	depends on OF && ARCH_SUNXI
	select RESET_CONTROLLER
	help
	  Clock gating, reset control and power domain management for the
	  Allwinner H713 TV subsystem (tvdisp, tvcap, tvfe blocks).

	  Required for display output on the HY310 projector. Manages
	  clocks and power for the display engine, TV capture (HDMI input),
	  and TV front-end (demodulator) subsystems.

	  Based on reverse engineering of stock sunxi_tvtop.ko from
	  H713 SDK V1.3 firmware.

	  If unsure, say Y.
